                    "value": "<p>The gorgon breathes a @Template[type:cone|distance:60] of green gas. Each creature in the area must attempt a @Check[type:fortitude|dc:25] save.</p>\n<p>The gorgon can't use Breath Weapon again for [[/br 1d4 #Recharge Breath Weapon]]{1d4 rounds}.</p>\n<hr />\n<p><strong>Critical Success</strong> The creature is unaffected.</p>\n<p><strong>Success</strong> The creature's body hardens and stiffens, causing it to become @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.Slowed]{Slowed 1} for 1 round.</p>\n<p><strong>Failure</strong> The creature becomes @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.Petrified] for 1 minute. It can attempt a new save at the end of each of its turns.</p>\n<p><strong>Critical Failure</strong> The creature becomes petrified permanently.</p>"
